The paper discusses an algorithm-hardware codesign for camera-based autonomous flight in small drones, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses transfer learning (TL) and reinforcement learning (RL) in the context of deep convolutional networks, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the use of on-die SRAM for real-time updates, which is a topic in embedded systems (cs.ET) and control systems (cs.SY).
